# Claude Code
.claude/settings.local.json

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Session checkpoints (transient — regenerated on every /project:checkpoint)
docs/wiki/session-checkpoint.md

# Planner plan files (transient — overwritten each cycle, not needed after implementation)
